long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Download JSON from Google Sheets.

Easy one-click download of your Google Sheets data as JSON file.


Effortlessly fetch your Google Sheets data and convert it into JSON files. Ideal for seamless integration with other applications or for maintaining your data in a highly portable format.

Instructions
1. Just click the "JSON" button in the toolbar in sheet you want to download.
2. The JSON file will be downloaded to your computer.

A free tool provided by sheet2api.com.
